            "title": "盤中速報 - 富國銀行(WFC-US)大跌5.06%，報88.83美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富國銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WFC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WFC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WFC-US</a>)截至台北時間14日22:31股價下跌4.73美元，報88.83美元，跌幅5.06%，成交量1,470,566（股），盤中最高價90.80美元、最低價88.82美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.02%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.83%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.08%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>富國銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WFC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WFC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WFC-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.48%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.37%</li> <li>近 3 月：+20.32%</li> <li>近 6 月：+13.82%</li> <li>今年以來：-0.25%</li></ul></section></main>",
